{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220410/extras/CapsulaAbout_v01.png?t=1733356384\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Free the refrigerator from bacteria as you punch, kick, and clean your way through the floors in this platformer, adventure, and action game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Frozen Injustice: Fridge Adventures</strong> is a game that brings out the best aspects of the action-platformer genre, creating a unique and enjoyable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are <strong>Broco-Lee</strong>, a trainee from Master Turnip-Man\u2019s Kung Fu Dojo, who, after completing his training, must use his cleaning powers to save the Refrigerator from the dreaded bacteria that are invading it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220410/extras/broco_punch.gif?t=1733356384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To fulfill your mission, you will need to fight bacteria, clean areas, and rescue innocent vegetables. Explore the different floors of the Fridge and solve the mystery that is infecting it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll meet colorful characters who will accompany you on your adventure, along with all the vegetables you\u2019ll save as you clean the areas. The more vegetables you rescue, the more allies you will have in this battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This vast and diverse world needs your help. Fight, grow, and learn. Become the cleaning hero the Refrigerator needs. Join the dojo!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733356384","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220410/page.bg.jpg?t=1733356384","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.s